function greetUser(name, greeting = "Hello") {
  return greeting + " " + name;
}

console.log(greetUser("Rohan"));
console.log(greetUser("Rohan", "Good Morning"));


OUTPUT: 
Hello Rohan
Good Morning Rohan

APPROACH:

Create function greetUser(name, greeting).

Set default parameter greeting = "Hello".

Return combined greeting message.
